N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 205.14 - Exemptions

State Regulations

Any grower whose aggregate number of planted acres of
cabbage in production in the marketing season is less than five shall be exempt
from reporting and payment for that marketing season. Notes
